title: Week 12 NFL Picks Against the Spread (Football 11/23)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Pete Prisco and R.J. White to break down every single game on the Week 12 weekend NFL slate against the spread, including: Browns-Bengals (6:30), Giants-Eagles (9:40), 49ers-Buccaneers (12:30), Packers-Vikings (16:10), Jaguars-Bills (19:30), Cardinals-Chargers (22:45), Seahawks-Panthers (24:30), Dolphins-Colts (28:30), Titans-Texans (31:45), Raiders-Ravens (33:05), Patriots-Jets (35:00) and Steelers-Broncos (36:40).
 
To learn more about listener data and our privacy practices visit: https://www.audacyinc.com/privacy-policy
